# 11. STYLES  --  Tailwind utility classes + custom keyframes (app/globals.css)
# =============================================================================
# intent: the widget is styled entirely with Tailwind utility classes inline in
# components/LiveChat.tsx plus TWO custom keyframe animations declared in
# app/globals.css. There is NO CSS module / SCSS file — port the class strings
# below and the keyframes and the widget looks identical in another Tailwind
# project. Icons are FontAwesome (faHeadset/faTimes/faComments/faPaperPlane/
# faSpinner/faCircleExclamation). Fixed bottom-right, z-50, above app chrome.
